+ * fiemap_fill_next_extent - Fiemap helper function
+ * @fieinfo:	Fiemap context passed into ->fiemap
+ * @logical:	Extent logical start offset, in bytes
+ * @phys:	Extent physical start offset, in bytes
+ * @len:	Extent length, in bytes
